{
 "name": "RPlog_Serenella_Talks_To_Her_Mother",
 "title": "Serenella Talks to Her Mother",
 "summary": "Returning to a seedy Efavan City club after more than a year away, Serenella Jordain confronts her worn-down mother Lucinda, who runs the bar, and introduces her infant granddaughter Tara. The reunion is tense and raw: Serenella, now a successful cruiseship entertainment manager, hurls bitter accusations about her neglected, sleazy childhood while Lucinda absorbs the blows and admits she failed as a mother. Beneath the recrimination, Serenella presses her old, aching need to know her real father, and when she explains that paternity can now be tested by DNA, the stunned Lucinda finally resolves to help. Lucinda recounts the shameful night she slept with two young rebels -- a shy blond named Athor or Anath and an unnamed tall, dark recruit -- before a one-night stand left her pregnant, leaving three possible fathers. The two part on fragile, hopeful terms, agreeing to meet again the next morning so Lucinda can provide a sample of the loathsome Dex to test.",
